{"tid":1251762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警晚會數百人參與　示威者舉牌高叫「支持獨立調查」","createTime":"2019-06-22T16:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:44:03.000Z","uid":53003,"like":13,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d1aaefa51b723e50f0fa6323223171c563c604c9","tid":1251762,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190622/s00001/1561200580976/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2F1561200580976%2F&h=9e25a8fa&s={SIZE}\" />【逃犯條例-多圖】撐警晚會數百人參與-示威者舉牌高叫「支持獨立調查」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f4069389dc1b30ab1a30ef9c8ff2f0c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff4069389dc1b30ab1a30ef9c8ff2f0c0.jpg&h=a65f35c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數百人出席遮打花園撐警晚會。（朱韻斐攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f612fd21f95f854b75cac02d47b19836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff612fd21f95f854b75cac02d47b19836.jpg&h=e172363e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f6155114c98755910069841b1f4f2d44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff6155114c98755910069841b1f4f2d44.jpg&h=53fda6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f4ceb294b81753b203efbbb8a7f2a8c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff4ceb294b81753b203efbbb8a7f2a8c8.jpg&h=c86841ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f4ce9f909e35ceb7c23e8ea8dd012fc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff4ce9f909e35ceb7c23e8ea8dd012fc4.jpg&h=e31ae802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人舉牌要求成立獨立調查委員會調查集會衝突事件。（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f4cedb25c8dd51305670ccc9984ccccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff4cedb25c8dd51305670ccc9984ccccf.jpg&h=0e8c9e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從美國回流的李先生。（朱韻斐攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f4cec798ea82a16272248ea18d2fc62e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff4cec798ea82a16272248ea18d2fc62e.jpg&h=61fed308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台下有兩名男子互罵。黃先生（左）不滿警方6．12衝突當天用過量武力，另一男子即場駁斥，指全靠警察維持治安，否則情況將更惡劣（羅嘉凝攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f6137825974d0e9ffb90272b486cd5d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff6137825974d0e9ffb90272b486cd5d5.jpg&h=9aae475d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f6140a7ec9dda80f7729a33cfe2e4a31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff6140a7ec9dda80f7729a33cfe2e4a31.jpg&h=0277fb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f6149890d3c1c4b231b42715ef2fb033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff6149890d3c1c4b231b42715ef2fb033.jpg&h=0b2a685b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f82c8116ea0a1fab7df4fa90af02a7c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff82c8116ea0a1fab7df4fa90af02a7c7.jpg&h=1ae38eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f82dc408fe6a7855723b760351ab1905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff82dc408fe6a7855723b760351ab1905.jpg&h=3a2d8861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，兩名市民在場外拉起寫有香港人互助、愛護警隊及支持人權法的橫額，遭參與集會的人指罵。（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f65bc7c6e2319cda596715f381103993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff65bc7c6e2319cda596715f381103993.jpg&h=a1c5a51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣（右）（朱韻斐攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190622/s00001/f6ea07f8a7a21ecf91e37928fb9be82a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190622%2Fs00001%2Ff6ea07f8a7a21ecf91e37928fb9be82a.jpg&h=da660284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名參與集會的女童看過示威等片段後落淚，稱片中人是「暴徒」，李偲嫣（右）著女童母親安慰她。（朱韻斐攝）"},{"pid":"ae9e3932c0dcf191a3b2a4f8438a7377ff0840ed","tid":1251762,"uid":2419,"like":160,"dislike":0,"score":160,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"絲打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfab60f616a261141fd76a5f248aeac61c95fc3","tid":1251762,"uid":130695,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"一班垃圾 請得果幾百人"},{"pid":"2adc71effc917f6e9ca7ad24c514d7ddfeb64748","tid":1251762,"uid":66049,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"嗰位絲打好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adbfdfa211edbd016b85e55232c4010dd269594","tid":1251762,"uid":155818,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23024e300803d4136586b5077a2264dce348ab46","tid"